      "widgets_values": [
        "🚀  QUICK START  —  Z-Image-Turbo  AUTO  Dual-Mode\n\n▸ MODE A  (keyword → AI-expanded prompt)\n  1.  Type subject in ✍️ PromptEnhancer  [prompt_text]\n  2.  Click  Queue Prompt\n\n▸ SWITCH TO MODE B  (image reference)\n  1.  Set  🔀 Mode Switch  [index]  =  1\n  2.  Drop image into  📸 LoadImage\n  3.  Click  Queue Prompt\n\n↩  Back to Mode A:  set  [index]  =  0\n\n─────────────────────────────────────────────\n▸ ASPECT RATIO\n  📐 Latent Switch  [index]:\n    0  =  Landscape  1920 × 1088  (16:9)\n    1  =  Portrait   1088 × 1920  (9:16)\n─────────────────────────────────────────────\nBoth switches: just change a number.\nNo rewiring needed.\n─────────────────────────────────────────────\n▸ MODELS  (place in ComfyUI/models/)\n    unet/  z-image-turbo.safetensors\n    clip/  qwen_3_4b.safetensors\n    vae/   ae.safetensors\n  License: Apache 2.0\n\n  Auto-download on first Queue (~3 GB):\n    Qwen3-VL-2B-Instruct  (via QwenVL node)\n─────────────────────────────────────────────\nSampler:  er_sde · beta · 9 steps · cfg 1.0\nGuidance:  FluxGuidance = 2\nSampling:  ModelSamplingAuraFlow shift=3\nOutput:  ComfyUI/output/z_image_turbo/\n─────────────────────────────────────────────\n⚠️  REQUIRED EXTENSION for er_sde sampler:\n    ComfyUI-ExtraSamplers  (https://github.com/Clybius/ComfyUI-Extra-Samplers)\n    Install via ComfyUI Manager: search \"Extra Samplers\""
